      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_dao_ren",
      "text": "现在长安城里，要杀他的人也不知道有多少，他简直已死定了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "玉箫道人",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "玉容，还不为伊先生斟酒？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我在这里牵制住他们，你去救人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
