      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在我们希望他追到这里来，就算他不来，我也会去找他的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "若不是你，我是真不知道该怎么样才能让那女孩子说实话。",
