      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "要女人说实话并不难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "一个女人的衣服若突然被撕光，很少还有敢不说实话的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "看不出你对付女人也很有经验。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我练的并不是童子功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "像你这样的男人，想练童子功只怕都很难。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她是不是被人点了哑穴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
