    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我认得你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "追……追她回来。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已杀了叶开，我已杀了叶开……",
      "tone": "疯狂",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "丁姑娘，跟我回去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是别人的家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "是谁的家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是个做茶叶买卖的生意人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你受的伤很重，我怕玉箫他们找来，只有带你赶快走。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "所以你就闯到这人家里来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这里的主人你当然也不认得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "现在他们的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "已被我杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是我本来并不想杀他们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我闯进来的时候，有两个人睡在床上，我本来以为他们是夫妇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "难道他们不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那女的已有三十多岁，男的却最多只有十七八，我逼着他们一问，这孩子就说了实话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我也希望你明白一件事。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "若有人认为你这样做的不对，认为你是个心狠手辣的女人，那人一定是个伪君子，是个大混蛋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我希望你相信我，我绝不是这种混蛋。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "药可以人口了，你喝下去好不好？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这是我自己配的药，我不敢找大夫，我怕别人会从大夫嘴里查出你的行踪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我遇见你，真的是运气，无论什么事你好像都能想得到。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但我却还是想不到她为什么要杀你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我想……她一定有原因的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "江湖中有很多邪门外道的事，我说给你听，你也未必知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你难道连一点都不怪她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "她这么样做，一定是被摄心术一类的邪法所迷，等她清醒后，她一定会比我更痛苦，我怎么还能怪她？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你在哭？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你为什么忽然伤心？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我并不是伤心，我只不过在想，假如有一天，能有个人这么样对我，处处都替我想，那么我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我出去才两个月，你就敢在家里偷人了，你难道不怕我宰了你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我问你，你为什么要做这种见不得人的事，这野男人是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "text": "你……你是不是看错人了？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我看错了人？你十六岁就嫁给了我，就算烧成了灰，我也认得你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "text": "你疯了，我连见都没有见过你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你难道还敢不承认是我的老婆？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "text": "当然不是。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你若不是我的老婆，为什么睡在我的床上？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你又是什么东西了为什么和我老婆睡在床上？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_shang_zhang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "茶叶商人",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "幸好我是个宽大为怀的人，不管你们做了什么事，我都原谅了你们，但现在我既然已回来了，你总该起来把这热被窝让给了我吧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不是他的老婆，我根本不认得他，你千万不能起来让他。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    }
